{"tid":1313082,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警隊真係有需要重組過。。（由細到大冇話憎警察）","createTime":"2019-07-13T16:17:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T01:13:13.000Z","uid":105590,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"395fda1c85510e894ad6bbabb893e22cd8f219d5","tid":1313082,"uid":105590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T16:17:18.000Z","msg":"雖然一直以黎都知道警察係低學歷人士做既職業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但本來都冇在意啲乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但近日一連串既警察暴打市民既事件 都令我確信左一件事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就係俾一班低學歷，冇思想，冇道德觀既爛仔（如果做唔到警察你重做到啲乜？）攞到武力係幾咁錯既事！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以警隊有必要重組！白衫既變哂藍衫！再請啲高學歷既phd去做白衫先正確！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講真由細都大冇話憎啲警察 但真係由呢啲事上面乜都睇到哂, 改觀哂<br />\n<br />\n而家出到街見到你地班黑警都真係驚無端白事會俾你地捉左去 最好你地唔好再係市民面前出現啦<br />\n<br />\n同埋真係而家先知原來咁多黑警咁賤格 成日上網撩啲女仔做sp 重原來有個白衫約條女上警處office扑野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係成個警隊都就黎冇野道德可言架啦<br />\n<br />\n你地今晚Sip高枕頭反省下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb402fba5cbd4c70ff302693245256ae5b64a327","tid":1313082,"uid":277186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T16:18:27.000Z","msg":"PhD 大把工做啦 駛撚賣良心"},{"pid":"87bf75a46a50d57d28d97f492e9c6b3f9e00b4ae","tid":1313082,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T16:19:28.000Z","msg":"印度女仔教你防衛術<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1313085\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1313085</a>"},{"pid":"4865ff7c97fc1ee552fd02cf046227db3f9c7a21","tid":1313082,"